	<article id="post-3844" class="post-3844 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-current-affairs category-democracy category-intelligence category-iraq category-law category-media category-national-security category-politics category-rttv category-snowden category-spies category-tv category-war-2 category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-alternative-media tag-annie-machon tag-crosstalk tag-hearts-and-minds tag-media-2 tag-peter-lavalle tag-rt tag-wikileaks">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/06/new-versus-old-media-rt-crosstalk-debate.html" title="Permalink to New v old media — RT Crosstalk debate" rel="bookmark">New v old media — <span class="caps">RT</span> Crosstalk debate</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/06/new-versus-old-media-rt-crosstalk-debate.html" title="15:42" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-06-30T15:42:27+00:00" pubdate>June 30, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/06/new-versus-old-media-rt-crosstalk-debate.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
