				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/2014" rel="tag">2014</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/chelsea-manning" rel="tag">Chelsea Manning</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/collateral-murder" rel="tag">collateral murder</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/integrity" rel="tag">integrity</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/iraq" rel="tag">Iraq</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/oxford-union-society" rel="tag">Oxford Union Society</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/saaii-award" rel="tag">SAAII Award</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/sam-adams" rel="tag">Sam Adams</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/war" rel="tag">war</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>			</span>
						
